scripts.generate-types: curl -L -o openapi.json 'https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/r/plugins/gitiles/mediawiki/extensions/Wikibase/+/refs/heads/REL1_44/repo/rest-api/src/openapi.json?format=TEXT' && base64 -d openapi.json > openapi.decoded.json && openapi-typescript openapi.decoded.json --output index.d.ts --only-types; rm -f openapi.json openapi.decoded.json
